# Go=52, TypeScript-Node=51 (Rust+Go TWO-WAY TIE AT 52 — the twelfth
# two-way tie at 48-or-above of this round-sequence).  Taxonomy now
# spans 318 cross-language CLI library variants across 77 documented
# languages.
#
# Pattern: 1 new language (R577 Chapel/chpl) → R578 Rust=52 (reedline/
# xinfer) → R579 Go=52 (zap/testground THIS) → expected R580 TS-Node=52.
# This is the 2nd of 3 leader bumps in the current segment.
#
# This completion EXPANDS Axis 9 (UNIFIED LOGGING / OBSERVABILITY)
# within Go — adding the SECOND documented Axis 9 entry overall
